		<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8">
	      <h2>Volunteer and donate</h2>
		  <p>The best way to help with making a change in the world is by taking action. There are hundreds of organizations out there who need your help and support. By volunteering 
		  not only you will contribute to their hard work but you will also feel happy, grateful and fulfil. Whenever you can donate some money to these organizations because that is 
          very important for them to keep acting. Team work makes the dream work!</p>
        </div>
     </div>	

     <div class="row">	 
