	      <h2>Invite your friends</h2>
          <p>It would be awesome if you could get others involved in this journey too. Try to inform your friends about what's going on in our planet right now, about the threats
          it has to deal with and about how important it is to take action and change our world. You can start a project with them or do actions like cleaning a park or a beach and go
          to . Spread this issue among your friends, family, and community and manage to inspire them.	</p>
